am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/legendward/brink.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Bard Question #1 - Dragons</span><hr size=1> I see a lot of bards swinging all manner of metalwork at dragons (SSoYs, Partizans, that thing that looks like a bicycle frame, etc etc). Bearing in mind the little damage we do (yeah, I turn off &quot;all others' hits&quot; to make me feel better too <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ), I assume the songs you sing are not instrument-based.<br>
<br>
I've been on 4 raids (2 vs each) and each time I've twisted elemental and guardian rhythms (with drum) to give me and my group +134 MR and +67 CR/FR. I'm nearing the end of 46th, so Niv's is probably going to feature heavily in what I sing next time.<br>
<br>
I've seen all sorts come up on the battlespam, including &quot;...lets out a huge bellow&quot; (gimme a break).<br>
<br>
The question is: what are you singing while you wave these bits of metal at the bad guys? <p><b>Brinklith Rioghbhardan</b> - Jester of Avalon<br>
<a href="http://www.geocities.com/mastersofavalon" target="_blank">Masters of Avalon</a><br>
Bard of Bristlebane<br>
<a href="http://www.brellserilis.net" target="_blank">Brell Serilis Server</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/unillon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nillon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>GD RPers</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(9/6/00 1:09:17 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Bard Question #1 - Dragons</span><hr size=1> I haven't been on a dragon raid with a bard in a while, but they always twisted resist songs when they did, using bellow is stupid because you're not going to get any magic based songs to stick. <p>Nillon, level 58 Myrmidon, Brell Serilis</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/uquemnwyndrunner.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Quemn Wyndrunner</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(9/6/00 1:52:59 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   no weapons!</span><hr size=1> dont use a weapon on a dragon raid!!!!!!!<br>
